></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Installing Autonom control minds into our factories boosts efficiency, reduces waste and aids worker well-being. [br/][br/]Your colonies gain {ProductionModefier} [production/] per worker in [productionSlot/]. In addition your colonies gain {HappinessAmount}[happiness/].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Instalacja świadomości sterujących Autonomii w naszych fabrykach zwiększy wydajność, zmniejszy ilość odpadów i poprawi nastrój robotników. [br/][br/]Twoje kolonie uzyskają {ProductionModefier} [production/] na robotnika w [productionSlot/]. Dodatkowo kolonia uzyska {HappinessAmount}[happiness/].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String"> 'Your' in this case refers to the player who can be either male or female.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AUTONOM_SPAWNER_SPECIAL01</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">#PP.K3.34 Transmission Terminal</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Terminal nadawczy #PP.K3.34</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AUTONOM_SPAWNER_SPECIAL02</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">#PT.F5.2B Transmission Terminal</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Terminal nadawczy #PT.F5.2B</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AUTONOM_SPAWNER_SPECIAL03</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">#TT.I4.12 Transmission Terminal</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Terminal nadawczy #TT.I4.12</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AUTONOM_SPAWNER_SPECIAL04</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">#KK.K9.1N Transmission Terminal</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Terminal nadawczy #KK.K9.1N</Da